      "note" : [ {
        "text" : "In Afghanistan, it's common to greet with a handshake, followed by placing your hand over your heart. In some cases, for instance when greeting older men or women, greeting with just a hand over your heart may be appropriate. In addition, this gesture might be used to express heartfelt gratitude for something.",
